---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you create an account, we collect your email address and password (stored securely using one-way hashing). When you submit a review, we collect information about your rental experience including move-in/move-out dates, ratings, and written feedback.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How We Protect Your Privacy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Fuzzy dates:</strong> We only display the season and year of your tenancy (e.g., "Fall 2024"), never exact dates.</li>
          <li><strong>Anonymous reviews:</strong> Your email and identity are never displayed publicly with your reviews.</li>
          <li><strong>Secure storage:</strong> Passwords are hashed and all data is stored securely.</li>
          <li><strong>No selling data:</strong> We never sell your personal information to third parties.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To display anonymous reviews to help other tenants</li>
          <li>To calculate aggregate ratings for buildings and landlords</li>
          <li>To contact you about your account or reviews if necessary</li>
          <li>To prevent fraud and abuse of the platform</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use essential cookies to keep you logged in and maintain your session. We do not use tracking cookies or share data with advertisers.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You can request to delete your account and all associated reviews at any time by contacting us. You can also update your email address through your account settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at privacy@ratemyplace.org.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
